{"tid":2360913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金唱片2021︱TWICE子瑜企正中曬腿　GOT7不續約新聞搶鏡","createTime":"2021-01-10T07:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:33:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ab2535ffbba98890a93a8ad2b1243411c92a1b","tid":2360913,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"《第35屆金唱片獎》（金唱片2021）唱片部門頒獎禮今天（10日）舉行，BTS防彈少年團、TWICE、SEVENTEEN和NCT 127等歌手都有出席，並由李多熙及成始璄擔任主持。由於今天有可能是GOT7團體的最後行程，因此關注度相當大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210110/424955354254675968960471.jpeg/qzsvHFj2VTtyvOcoa468VL2tOZk4PxeN_f3unv397p4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210110%2F424955354254675968960471.jpeg%2FqzsvHFj2VTtyvOcoa468VL2tOZk4PxeN_f3unv397p4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=33eee70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於昨天紅地氈，今天只有TWICE和(G)I-DLE兩組女團參與，雖然有BTS防彈少年團等加持，但始終較失色。不過講到今天的焦點，必定是今天較早時間爆出全員不續約的GOT7，在合約完結前，這有可能將是組合最後的團體行程。不過從現場照片可見，雖然似乎7人心情都未有被報道影響，但粉絲已叫定不捨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210110/424955533410177024092514.jpeg/uctlo1eHLe_FurJFuCPclECvaccZYKRSGcz12RnM9dk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210110%2F424955533410177024092514.jpeg%2Fuctlo1eHLe_FurJFuCPclECvaccZYKRSGcz12RnM9dk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ca024629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec0f2eca96109849b24a4acbfde55ddc21a253e3","tid":2360913,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210110/424955764679905280103845.jpeg/F2tnFz9CSS46XcXpxYWudJpkWS-J10XAEzowNBM6MDQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210110%2F424955764679905280103845.jpeg%2FF2tnFz9CSS46XcXpxYWudJpkWS-J10XAEzowNBM6MDQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3493a144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.h